extendedInfo.description: An official app of McCullough-Hyde Memorial Hospital. You can use the app to find health care providers, read health news, search for health information, learn more about the services we offer, and access maps and contact information.A community hospital in Oxford Ohio serving the needs of Miami University students, faculty and staff and residents of Butler and  Preble counties in Ohio and Franklin and Union counties in Indiana. A full service hospital including world-class emergency room, Orthopedics, General Surgery, Cardiology, Maternity and a broad array of inpatient and outpatient services.
